\c 31
\s Egipita haingabatsiri, asi Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Vane nhamo vanoburukira Egipita kundotsvaka kubatsirwa, vanotenda mabhiza, vanovimba nengoro dzokurwa nekuti izhinji, uye navatasvi vamabhiza nekuti vane simba kwazvo, asi havatariri kuno Mutsvene waIsiraeri, kana kutsvaka Jehovha.
\v 2 Kunyange zvakadaro naiye akachenjera, achauyisa nhamo, haangadzosi mashoko ake, asi achamukira imba yavanoita zvakaipa, navanobatsirana navanoita zvakaipa.
\v 3 Zvino vaEgipita vanhu, havazi Mwari, namabhiza avo inyama, haazi mweya; zvino kana Jehovha achitambanudza ruoko rwake, anobatsira achagumburwa nowanobatsirwa achawira pasi, vose vachapera pamwechete.
\p
\v 4 nekuti zvanzi naJehovha kwandiri, Zvakaita seshumba nomwana weshumba zvinoombera chayabata; kunyange vafudzi vazhinji vakakokerwa kuzorwa nayo, haingavhunduswi namanzwi avo. haingavi nehanya nokupopota kwavo; saizvozvo Jehovha wehondo achaburukira pamusoro pegomo reZiyoni napamusoro pechikomo charo kuzorwa navo.
\v 5 Seshiri dzinodzengerera, saizvozvo Jehovha achatavirira Jerusarema; acharitavirira nokurirwira, acharidarika nokurisunungura.
\p
\v 6 Dzokerai kuna iye wamakamukira zvikuru, imwi vana vaIsiraeri.
\v 7 nekuti nezuva iro mumwe nomumwe ucharasha zvifananidzo zvake zvesirivha nezvifananidzo zvake zvendarama, zvamakazviitira namaoko enyu, zvikava zvivi kwamuri.
\v 8 Ipapo muAsiria achawa nomunondo usati uri womunhu; munondo usati uri wavanhu uchamudya; achatiza pamberi pomunondo, namajaya ake achabatirwa chibharo.
\v 9 Dombo rake richatiza nokutya, machinda ake achavhunduswa nomureza, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, anomoto wake paZiyoni, nechoto chake paJerusarema.
